examples.en: The region has higher educational attainment than the nation as a whole.
This scholarship is given for promise, rather than for attainment.
Her scientific attainments have made her quite well-known in the field of biology.
She values educational attainment above all else.
His attainment of puberty was delayed by malnutrition.
